        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="feat-item" itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem">
        <meta itemprop="position" content="9">
        <div class="feat-ic" style="background:var(--orange-bg);color:var(--orange)"><i class="fa-solid fa-flag"></i></div>
        <div class="feat-body">
          <span class="feat-num">09</span>
          <h3 itemprop="name">Ticket Prioritization</h3>
          <p itemprop="description">Auto-prioritize tickets based on customer tier, issue type, and SLA urgency for smarter triage.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="feat-item" itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem">
        <meta itemprop="position" content="10">
        <div class="feat-ic" style="background:var(--green-bg);color:var(--green)"><i class="fa-solid fa-note-sticky"></i></div>
        <div class="feat-body">
          <span class="feat-num">10</span>
          <h3 itemprop="name">Internal Notes</h3>
          <p itemprop="description">Private team notes on tickets for internal collaboration without exposing comments to customers.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="feat-item" itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem">
        <meta itemprop="position" content="11">
        <div class="feat-ic" style="background:var(--pink-bg);color:var(--pink)"><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-column"></i></div>
        <div class="feat-body">
          <span class="feat-num">11</span>
          <h3 itemprop="name">Reporting & Analytics</h3>
          <p itemprop="description">Response time, resolution time, and agent performance metrics to identify bottlenecks and improve.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="feat-item" itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem">
        <meta itemprop="position" content="12">
        <div class="feat-ic" style="background:var(--cyan-bg);color:var(--cyan)"><i class="fa-solid fa-object-group"></i></div>
        <div class="feat-body">
          <span class="feat-num">12</span>
          <h3 itemprop="name">Parent-Child Tickets</h3>
          <p itemprop="description">Link related tickets together and track them as a group for complex issues that span multiple requests.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pwhy">
